### Upload PDF → JPG (default options: dpi=200, quality=85)
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-jpg
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Upload PDF → JPG (custom: dpi=300, quality=100)
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-jpg?dpi=300&quality=100
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Upload PDF → JPG (low quality: dpi=72, quality=50)
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-jpg?dpi=72&quality=50
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
